{"tid":1780423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會屬下「政府人員協會」竟綁架全港公務員，反對獨立審議警察加薪，要全港公務員加薪無望","createTime":"2019-12-12T10:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T10:53:15.000Z","uid":230104,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfe3f7fddae5841cead6c2ef11c3cdea048d53e","tid":1780423,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:51:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>立即成立對沖工會，將工聯會打殘</strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n反修例風波下，警方執法成為政治爭議核心之一，有民主派議員要求立法會財務委員會在審議公務員加薪撥款時，抽起警隊加薪分開處理。工聯會「政府人員協會」昨日（11日）去信立法會財委會，指反對將警務人員薪酬調整抽起獨立審議，過往沒有這種先例，要求全香港公務員同警察共進退。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府人員協會屬工聯會屬會，政治立場親建制，<span style=\"color: red;\">曾公開批評民主派公務員於8月初的集會不符政治中立，但呼籲公務員參與由守護香港大聯盟舉辦的「反暴力，救香港」集會。</span>"},{"pid":"3daf52be5fce9c8210458be3a92bb27dfa873f81","tid":1780423,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"又係唔揪得搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adeea6ed66b4b84932aa3f0ce3bdd28a8ca6fe55","tid":1780423,"uid":165749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"都係啲黑警累事啦"},{"pid":"a664b3734a9f3430034ad56102d5d857dbb40abb","tid":1780423,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"611cfe7b2b5b12bce202d3047492fcf842c6d3bc","tid":1780423,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"整個「反警暴，救香港」集會咪參加囉"},{"pid":"f63a7cd4ada8b7b28301c5b1bae453a6ba2481e3","tid":1780423,"uid":317979,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmyweNU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmyweNU.png&h=0e86c2da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"283e42a13e2f3727c969b58623915a074c94fb37","tid":1780423,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"